comment.narrative:
1. Curriculum & Learning Materials Development: Completion of 6 initial SDG Leadership Certification Modules and 12 SDG Mobile Learning Modules, engaging SMEs and external module reviewers, Hiring Course Instructors (in collaboration with SDGs Hub UI);
2. Learning Management System & Massive Open Online Course: Working with multimedia vendors to digitize contents from SDGs Hub UI, Conducting User Acceptance Test (UAT) to finalize both LMS and MOOC platforms;
3. Brand Identification, Communication, and Partnership with Stakeholders: conducting Webinars to further promote the Academy and increase the database from various stakeholders (Government, Private Sectors, Students, Academicians, NGO, philanthropy, UN and other Int. Org, Media, etc) to reach out to various stakeholders and potential participants, as well as exploring potential collaboration with relevant stakeholders; and
4.	Final list of 1st intake participants.

